abstract: >-
  A local-first AI runtime implementing Answer Entitlement Architecture:
  it determines whether answering is justified before generating a response,
  combining retrieval and evidence verification over a multilingual FAISS/ME5
  Wikipedia index. Runs locally via Ollama or against cloud backends.
